Data.title: 4K Image Upscaler
Data.author: Alex
Data.metadata: Enhanced Deep Residual Networks for Single Image Super-Resolution (EDSR)
Data.description: Built using Python and Streamlit, this application takes an input image and returns and upscaled 2K, and 4K resolution of the same image. Although the application can accept any image, drawings are prefered as they're easier for the algorithms to work with and require less time to upscale.
